{"tid":1297901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜攻勢！趕絕中國旅客！由自己做起！全城霸講普通話！","createTime":"2019-07-08T17:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T19:37:57.000Z","uid":66390,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ff12cd8efbca5a446c2b78ff3918141a836a91a0","tid":1297901,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"各位連登仔好！<br />\n<br />\n第一波行動！<span style=\"color: red;\">趕絕中國旅客 由霸講普通話做起！</span><br />\n<br />\n作為香港人 有自己本土語言 普通話又唔係國際語言 點解要遷就人地？ 唔識講廣東話okay! 要講就講國際語言 英文！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1. 工作時 堅拒講普請話</ins></strong><br />\n如果你份工需要接觸中國人 <span style=\"color: red;\">由今天開始 只用廣東話/英語</span><br />\n如果你係呢類人 eg sales 你一定會聽過 <span style=\"color: red;\">「聽不懂」「你說什麼」</span>等等既嚴重捲舌支那語<br />\n點解佢地會肆無忌憚咁一來香港 就老憑講普通話？ 就係因為佢地覺得香港人識普通話 會講普通話 <br />\n亦因為咁 佢地經常以自由行方式來香港！（其他原因eg近 暫不詳談）唔見自由行橫遍歐美？<br />\n<br />\n其實好簡單！佢一來講普通話 你就話：我聽唔明 你講返廣東話 香港人要先快過佢地一步講「我聽唔明」<br />\n佢地就會以一句「哦」就會離去 / 會用廣東話溝通（呢一刻就會心諗 屌 識講既 之後你就可以搵下一個target<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n呢個做法 目的就係要重新建立<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人只對中國人不禮貌之形象</span><br />\n<br />\n你一個肯咁做 就真係好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">分享一個岩岩經歷既例子 話說我岩岩經過一間鋪 個Sales堅持講廣東話問佢要唔要膠袋 個中國客就係咁話聽唔明 最後個sales就無計$0.5 最尾個西客就話要袋 個sales就黑尻佢面 點知條仆街竟然話「你不會說普通話嗎？」 個sales就著撚左用普通話講「那你不會說廣東話嗎？ 這裡是香港」 我隨即給予掌聲</span><br />\n<br />\n如果法國人高傲 堅持用法文 唔用英語 大家都會想排法 唔再去法國 會認為法國人<span style=\"color: red;\">無禮貌</span><br />\n<br />\n只要廣泛咁做 佢地自然會減少來港次數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2. 街道 問對方身份 繼而拒答</ins></strong><br />\n中國傻西瓜連google map都唔會知係咩<br />\n成日衝來衝去搵路 一句唔該都無就會彈句<span style=\"color: red;\">「在哪裡呀」「怎樣去啊」？</span><br />\n<br />\n我建議大家可以：<span style=\"color: red;\">問一問對方邊到人（雖然你明知係支那人）佢答完之後 你就隨即反應：「哦 那88」「中國人？我不會幫」等等</span><br />\n<br />\n目的就係要<span style=\"color: red;\">我擺明唔幫支那人</span><br />\n唔好同我講咩一視同仁呢啲老土野啦<br />\n我擺到明係歧視！<br />\n令佢地對香港旅遊更反感<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>「小心！」3.  小心分辦台灣人與中國人</ins></strong><br />\n大家咁撚醒目 一定分到<br />\n<br />\n大概分為<br />\n(i) 語氣表達：台灣人講野比較溫柔 唔會捲到十八灣咁撚樣 <br />\n(ii) 發音用詞：eg 「垃圾」兩國發音都唔同<br />\n(iii) 行為 文化<br />\n(iv) 樣貌<br />\n(v) 衣著<br />\n<br />\niI i-v 都唔多講 大家一定化左灰都識分<br />\n<br />\n呢家香港同台灣 we connect 左<br />\n唔好分化 小心對待講「中文/國語」既台灣人<br />\n多啲留意<br />\n唔sure咪問佢係邊到人<br />\n話中國/內地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪轉返廣東話囉<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家記得</strong><br />\n目的就係要<span style=\"color: red;\">創造香港人只對中國人不禮貌既形象</span> 可能本身都有 但唔夠<span style=\"color: red;\">全城！</span><br />\n所以一定要打造<span style=\"color: red;\">全城霸講普通話！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係一條link<br />\n講述中國旅客因港人不禮貌 而轉戰澳門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190502/59551842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190502%2F59551842&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=39722378\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190502%2F59551842&h=ff430d7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190502/59551842</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有啲要跑數/個人賺中國旅客錢 就另計啦<br />\n但收工遇問路 一樣可以！<br />\n<br />\n有人可能會話<strong>中國旅客減少會影響經濟</strong><br />\n屌啦 咁多年呀！賺夠多啦 有冇份袋入小市民袋呀？佢地更加放肆來香港 炒呢樣炒個樣 炒到民不聊生！<br />\n如果真係差 我情願攬炒！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一波：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">13/7（六）光復上水！</span>"},{"pid":"2a7822f009afd6fe8c42b3d6dca056cc09e19182","tid":1297901,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38b7083e3cc62e224af79353c983da68d0032646","tid":1297901,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全城開火！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e807a321df5a3544302032f92f7fae9bc2574696","tid":1297901,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af0b01d5a03ba6c3e8d0183cdcee9d9394b2ad5","tid":1297901,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9298304894f45f11ba285de6aea2437dcac8de","tid":1297901,"uid":45161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\nBtw係「罷」"},{"pid":"3a0420c4d7bd7afbf576b68ea8c4c536499788e2","tid":1297901,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec9298304894f45f11ba285de6aea2437dcac8de","tid":1297901,"uid":45161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\nBtw係「罷」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝"},{"pid":"55ad3d52540bbdc8fe5b1a627136178b81c5eb19","tid":1297901,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec9298304894f45f11ba285de6aea2437dcac8de","tid":1297901,"uid":45161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\nBtw係「罷」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"好撚7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />標題都錯"},{"pid":"46a7cb09ed892245ae0a6e4fb54cfc466445fafa","tid":1297901,"uid":53848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:13:08.000Z","msg":"「霸」講同「罷」講完全相反喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f14b5ee22a1d8a1443ab179139896dee3cca07","tid":1297901,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:13:09.000Z","msg":"有用post請大力推<br />\n香港人要團結<br />\n<br />\n幫手推下面啲POST<br />\n（急求）７７義士被控襲警求片！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295985</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n急！！！ 我有個 旺角義士朋友 需要大家幫幫手拯救！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【突發】聽朝9點 屯門區議會 要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297048</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n白宮聯署，促盡快實施人權法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea79d5e56a4d7aaa95af589f5ae71b0f19f6a12d","tid":1297901,"uid":246419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:13:20.000Z","msg":"霸講定罷講呀ching"},{"pid":"a64ff8ef6d25e964ec77bcf85303f965729261b2","tid":1297901,"uid":66390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqNN7zm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqNN7zm.png&h=8bb9f88a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0aa7f4f6d0cd192c34b0ea74c80814f1fce71df","tid":1297901,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全港「罷講」普通話！"},{"pid":"273871e19dc7c8c4421181e5e2b8dbea9bcef554","tid":1297901,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"re